How to use this in intellij

1. Clone this any way you like and do File -> open project, and select the pom.xml
2. To use git via intellij you need to install the git plugin.
3. You can add a tomcat configuration via Run-> Edit Configuration -> + -> Tomcat Server -> Local -> Add example webapp under deployments tab.
4. Run it 

to check out via intellij doesn't work very well because of lacking support for submodules: http://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-64024


